# Byte-identity golden fixtures must never be line-ending-converted by
# core.autocrlf (which defaults to true on many Windows dev machines) --
# a CRLF-converted checkout would silently break exact-string comparisons
# against these files. See tests/engine/test_manager_context_prompt.py
# (Wave 2 review F2).
tests/engine/golden/*.txt text eol=lf
